                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-14-off76 t18170416-14-cd77"></join>, two pair of breeches, value 10s.; two pair of pantaloons, value 7s.; one jacket, value 5s.; one pair of trowsers, value 5s.; one shirt, value 2s., and one great coat, value 10s.
